<p>A long time ago, I wanted to make a Gundam 'beat em up. I even made a bunch of 32x32 animations for this purpose. That sounds small by today's "hi-bit" standards, but you can fit a lot of visual data in that space with the right colors. Never did make that game, tho.</p>
